ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes that identify patients with a diagnosis of cirrhosis or other liver disease.),(Data Element Scope: This value set is developed for the diagnosis QDM datatype. It can potentially be used for other datatypes as well.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include all diagnosis codes associated with cirrhosis or other liver disease.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exlcude diagnosis codes for neonatal and juvenile liver diseases.)
